Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你听到这段话时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.92,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(840,611)\blur2}（夏威夷生存圈）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22世纪 对人类来说已成战争时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:35.97,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,0)\blur2\pos(656,611)}（波莉亚胡运输基地）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自遥远宇宙的未知存在 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们拥有超越人类理解范围的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自40年前它们出现在这颗星球上以来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球大半土地都已化作战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落前60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照作战行动 迅速加入前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射板 确认固定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收导航信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射轨道 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aloha(你好) Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基斯可是连敌人都会调戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是想被它们调戏一下啊 金色外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是通过了严苛训练
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活至今的精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够与你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深以为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号机 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比报告说的还严重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.00,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,663)}Second machine Olympia-Angels,landing check
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号机 奥林匹亚天使 着陆检查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要像哥哥一样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五号机 出动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Festum专用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考控制体感操纵式有人兵器Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被选中的人才能开动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认类型1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意类型4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内置敌人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其力量为人类所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有Fafner 我们或许早就灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使胜利遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们争取到了足以获得希望的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩根机呼叫戈尔德队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始加入前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要通话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号转换全都被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层太小看敌人的读心能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人能读取我们的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒纳凯阿前哨基地陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有功能被敌人夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快疏导平民避难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有部队到北端集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一防卫队 溃灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距大岛最终防线还剩2千米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 纳雷因将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 这里是太平洋圈最大的运输基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦陷落将有数百万人饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要死守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前明明置之不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道学会了人类是如何保命的吗 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人都近在咫尺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 马上就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒纳凯阿没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十号机严重损坏 乔治遇害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要停下 按作战计划前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现戈尔德队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人 他们被敌人同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 切断罗伯的右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你·在·那·里·吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯 快脱离 罗伯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…侵入内心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬里尔…启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯 罗伯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部下达交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象为大岛全域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部指挥下的空袭部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通新国联总部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的名义下令中止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人侵入基地内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间运输机被击坠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同伴在作战啊 还有几万平民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交战规定α必须严守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺沃尔特少校的权限 逮捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳雷因将军发来中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入坐标 攻击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢将我的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员搜寻生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯芬克斯型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…攻击了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…还有人活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 我们赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…究竟是为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这疲于征战的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将诞生于世界一隅
