Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战乱毁灭了日本之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保留和平文化而建造的人工岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我曾经的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是地区对抗赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香知道了 要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香三香 你不用太起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 是咲良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们休息会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那孩子 就会想起以前的一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下班去一骑那里吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你不喜欢我做的菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马广登特别篇 追寻神秘巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了几个节目啊 白痴广登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹也太惯着他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 又闲又热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我想去ALVIS工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老学些战斗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要继承岛上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少开个空调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好 里奈学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你昨天不是买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是用来保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镝木 你是学生会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老买漫画 七夕祭都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个…里奈学姐不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议程就进展不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去一骑学长那里一起开会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 麻烦学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 里奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我可是在干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要局限于机体设计
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要培养实际组装的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机 改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.75,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,663)}Mk.Sechs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腕部驱动系统 组装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进行FTP实验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认连接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进步哦 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈教得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我是乘员兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里待一整天要憋出病来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去一骑那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓 都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不希望任何人再驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然又要组装这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到卡诺恩会去学当工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻本事可不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说想请教保叔你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是引退吧 还得继续画这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是驾驶员培训教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尾老师的要求可没法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去老地方吃咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗 赶不上午餐时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御门 给您搬到里面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老爸教我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这边了 一骑哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午的研究结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像还在准备 我等下再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,员工伙食就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 新产品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不过谁做的就冠谁的名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如一骑咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沟口叔擅自起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很尊敬一骑学长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见和沟口叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上 最近都没下来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为能和远见学姐一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天箭呼叫管制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:53.27,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,663)}Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪不明机体 输入导引装置信息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标F1（导弹发射）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷斯呼叫天箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:11.54,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,663)}Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快也不能把屁股送给敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又败给沟口叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是实战 被击坠的是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷斯 请求继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 天箭重新领航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵从指令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么叫我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你坐在大飞机上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕不怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽真是的 最近总是那样和空想的朋友说话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为没有其他同龄的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我觉得也不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感受性很强 总是令人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐飞机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了呢 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极其平庸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.27,0:24:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.01,0:24:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你什么叫烹饪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.76,0:24:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预定高了两度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.56,0:24:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要修正
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.22,0:24:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是 有够笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.73,0:24:56.64,note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\fad(400,0)\blur2}（营业中 特色午餐仅限今日）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.62,0:24:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐套餐两份对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加两杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.81,0:25:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.59,0:25:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是皆城炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.74,0:25:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好像很美味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.33,0:25:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.21,0:25:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.86,0:25:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总士也在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩的蜜瓜冰淇淋苏打 给
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.57,0:25:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赠品 给常客的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.06,0:25:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.16,0:25:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.16,0:25:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.89,0:25:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩30遍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次检查是下周 可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.39,0:25:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.58,0:25:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们的成人礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.55,0:25:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来帮忙准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.01,0:25:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.79,0:25:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是麻烦你 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:25:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.63,0:26:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.05,0:26:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心完我 又来担心一骑的身体了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.03,0:26:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.28,0:26:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是担心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.99,0:26:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微也做点自己喜欢的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.69,0:26:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.03,0:26:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如跟你吃饭什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.83,0:26:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见选了航空 卡诺恩选了工科
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.22,0:26:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司选了医疗 要则是教育
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.62,0:26:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都决定了前途
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.55,0:26:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士是搞研究吗 挺适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.84,0:26:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 就在咖啡厅做菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地挺合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.74,0:26:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不想浪费前王牌驾驶员的宝贵经验
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.44,0:26:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当教官也不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了Fafner也不会消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.15,0:26:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尼伯龙根连接造成的小规模同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.76,0:26:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会发现治疗方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.68,0:27:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学了什么 开始去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.85,0:27:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望它半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是这样吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.62,0:27:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有恢复的可能性 不要悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.94,0:27:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有悲观 还剩3年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么长时间 也能做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.34,0:27:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我眼睛也看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.22,0:27:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里那样平静 是重要的同伴曾经待过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.24,0:27:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.63,0:27:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士学长
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.13,0:27:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下层区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.37,0:27:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去人工生态圈实验室之前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.61,0:27:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去看看乙姬的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.29,0:27:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立上在攻读医学吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.74,0:27:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向特殊医疗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.87,0:28:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见老师说要照顾乙姬 两者都需要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.53,0:28:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.90,0:28:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.62,0:28:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乙姬为我们所做的相比
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.96,0:28:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界 还一直战争不断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.75,0:28:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据所罗门的应答 战火还在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬是那么地渴望和平
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.32,0:28:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.13,0:29:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 乙姫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.59,0:29:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直守护着岛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.77,0:29:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么了乙姫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.35,0:29:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对什么有反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.94,0:29:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC 不明机体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.66,0:29:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,90秒后将到达护盾防线
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.48,0:29:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标接触
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.22,0:29:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标遭遇 对照
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp2}C-300 超星系
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.06,0:29:45.65,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(707,663)\fs28\fscx90}Super Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.81,0:29:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类军大型运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.83,0:29:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.02,0:30:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.89,0:30:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.04,0:30:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很漂亮的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.83,0:30:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.43,0:30:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.94,0:30:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.90,0:30:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉似乎也感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.65,0:30:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让我们见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.55,0:30:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷斯呼叫CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.36,0:30:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.81,0:30:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天箭 追踪接触
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.41,0:30:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习中的红隼发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:02.77,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(641,663)}Kestrel
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.93,0:31:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军运输机正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.63,0:31:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护盾圈外确认到不明质量虫洞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.90,0:31:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门无应答
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.08,0:31:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全格纳库进入迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.03,0:31:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1 第2磁冠护盾已展开完成
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.91,0:31:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持航路 Fafner待机
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出手 敌人还未发现岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.19,0:31:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有人类军被追击
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.48,0:31:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住区请求通信
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.67,0:31:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.54,0:31:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.51,0:31:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.38,0:31:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.30,0:31:36.41,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}拜托 妈妈 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.45,0:31:37.86,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}没事的 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:40.87,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}冷静点 现在正在帮你拜托人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.00,0:31:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她说「请救救飞机」
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.41,0:31:45.10,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}今日计划出勤的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:48.04,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}请立即转移至紧急起飞状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.08,0:31:52.02,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}各位岛民请避免外出 等待新的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.06,0:31:54.37,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}伴随紧急起飞状态 第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.22,0:31:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 戈班真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.26,0:31:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗 你昨天不是也买了一样的杂志？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.43,0:31:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.93,0:31:59.56,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}第一种警戒态势(Waffe laden)已准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.60,0:32:02.70,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}向岛防卫队 刚瑠岛后格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.74,0:32:06.01,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}庆树岛格纳库部队 以及预备候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.05,0:32:10.34,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}请立即转移至待机室…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.75,0:31:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改成出击请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.23,0:32:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.29,0:32:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个视频照明不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.90,0:32:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不要做那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.82,0:32:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会再陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.08,0:32:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是实战 我们也能乘坐Fafner吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.29,0:32:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接测试都没做过？多半参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.18,0:32:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我还没像广登学长一样做好头盔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.94,0:32:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.39,0:32:23.71,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.23,0:32:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学长交托给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.72,0:32:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广登学长
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.36,0:32:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.96,0:32:36.04,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}已抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.81,0:32:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.57,0:32:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗 把护身符给人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.47,0:32:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能乘坐Fafner也只有几年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.26,0:32:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趁现在传承下去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.18,0:33:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.53,0:33:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能先出手攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.45,0:33:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.10,0:33:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.39,0:33:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人极有可能于200秒以内实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.51,0:33:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向50 速度减慢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.71,0:33:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除部分护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红隼引导运输机降落海面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.68,0:33:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CDC呼叫格雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按规定开始导航
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.29,0:33:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.32,0:33:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.49,0:33:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入代码
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.88,0:33:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.65,0:33:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.83,0:34:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫天箭 这是毕业测试
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.05,0:34:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.64,0:34:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫飞行中的C-300
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.30,0:34:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是FA3 代号天箭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.47,0:34:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.30,0:34:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢通信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是C-300 代号鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.97,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(798,663)}Ketos
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军南亚舰队所属
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.95,0:34:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊航空连队珀耳修斯中队
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.50,0:34:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫鲸鱼 请遵从导航
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.49,0:34:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫天箭 我方会全面遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.26,0:34:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为条件请转达贵方的指导者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.92,0:34:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们的要求是让双方的希望相遇」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.85,0:34:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.65,0:35:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以众多牺牲换来的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.45,0:35:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜抛弃它也要追寻的究竟为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.22,0:35:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随新的战争降临的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.45,0:35:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最后的时间 开始转动
